[Amit Varma]: chess. I think there is this interesting case that there is an addictive side to my nature.

01:00:29.280 --> 01:00:34.960
[Amit Varma]: And the question is, what outlet do I give it? And, you know, online chess is an interesting

01:00:34.960 --> 01:00:39.760
[Amit Varma]: outlet. And I, and I play online chess and chess.com. Like, do you want to find my name

