[Amit Varma]: on me, horny Indian boys keep hitting on me. And also, I probably win more games and I

01:00:48.600 --> 01:00:53.360
[Amit Varma]: should because of that. But I played at the way the fish used to play poker, the bad players

01:00:53.360 --> 01:00:57.640
[Amit Varma]: used to play poker, that is that I don't want to improve, I just, I'll play one minute games

01:00:57.640 --> 01:01:01.800
[Amit Varma]: for timepass, bullet or bullet or blitz games for timepass. And I don't want to improve.

01:01:01.800 --> 01:01:05.040
[Amit Varma]: So I don't want to work on my game, which is how a lot of people play poker back in

01:01:05.040 --> 01:01:08.660
[Amit Varma]: the day that they would not improve at all. While you know, the rest of us would study

01:01:08.660 --> 01:01:12.480
[Amit Varma]: a bit and we would discuss hands with other good players. What were the choices? What

01:01:12.480 --> 01:01:16.680
[Amit Varma]: do you think his range was? But bad players are just playing for the heck of it. And of

01:01:16.680 --> 01:01:20.960
[Amit Varma]: course, many bad players will make a show of going through the study, but not actually

01:01:20.960 --> 01:01:25.560
[Amit Varma]: do any of it. To answer that question, I think I think I am. I don't know if addictive is

01:01:25.560 --> 01:01:29.720
[Amit Varma]: the right word for it, because it's never gone beyond a certain limit. But I think I

01:01:29.720 --> 01:01:35.120
[Amit Varma]: am intense, where I'll, you know, get into something and just go all in. Like I've, I

01:01:35.120 --> 01:01:39.320
[Amit Varma]: went all in on podcasting, I went all in on blogging, and I'll, I'll just go all in into

01:01:39.320 --> 01:01:44.040
[Amit Varma]: things which is great. But what I need to do is I need to go and you know, with Kartika's

01:01:44.040 --> 01:01:49.240
[Amit Varma]: encouragement and help, I think I'm on my way to doing that now is go all in on actually

01:01:49.240 --> 01:01:54.060
[Amit Varma]: writing books, you know, not just a compilation like this is but actually go all in on writing

01:01:54.060 --> 01:01:57.920
[Amit Varma]: books, because everything that I've gone all in for while rewarding for its own sake and

