[Unknown]: but it's related to life.

01:04:34.680 --> 01:04:40.320
[Unknown]: Ah, the hunter becomes the hunted. So Amit, I had a question for you. I've always been

01:04:40.320 --> 01:04:45.760
[Unknown]: fascinated in sport by the interplay between skill and bluff. There are a lot of very skilled

