[Guest]: beginning. What made you start the scene and the unseen?

01:20:24.360 --> 01:20:31.080
[Amit Varma]: Yeah. So I mean, like I sort of mentioned in the intro, what really happened was that

01:20:31.080 --> 01:20:37.400
[Amit Varma]: this friend of mine called Amit Doshi, who runs IBM podcasts, podcasting network approached

