[Guest]: So in that sense, a lot of people are also listening, not because of I mean, in addition

01:28:46.120 --> 01:28:50.120
[Guest]: to the things you mentioned, it is passive, it doesn't compete. But it's because they

01:28:50.120 --> 01:28:55.360
[Guest]: may not know what to read yet. Right? Because they may not have had time to go to the bookstore

01:28:55.360 --> 01:29:00.400
[Guest]: or browse, you know, do things like what you and I do, or, in your case, in my case, we're

